Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直完美啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去玩
